 : properties) {\n            if (property.getName().equals(name)) {\n                return property;\n            }\n        }\n        throw new AssertionError(\"Missing field property: \" + name);\n    }\n\n    public static class ArrayProperties {\n        public String[] names = { \"first\", \"second\" };\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1446, "output": 902, "cacheRead": 16896, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 19244, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777448306239, "responseId": "resp_05015fcc2792531b0169f1b572fff881958038304945505174"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_oTQZRF9K33ncewv90rnwqZ6H|fc_05015fcc2792531b0169f1b579dadc8195969f6ae13389d425", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1823 bytes to tests/src/org.hibernate.common/hibernate-commons-annotations/5.1.2.Final/src/test/java/org_hibernate_common/hibernate_commons_annotations/JavaXArrayTypeTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777448317048}]}
